A warm, sunlit living room scene in Studio Ghibli style showing two young children with bright, excited expressions huddled over a colorful board game spread across a low wooden table. The board game depicts a winding snowy mountain slope with tiny ski figures positioned along the path. Scattered around are playful dice and game pieces. The children's faces glow with wonder and discovery, their small fingers pointing at different spots on the board. Through a large window behind them, cherry blossoms drift past. The room has cozy details like cushions, a steaming teapot, and soft afternoon light casting gentle shadows. The overall mood is joyful, innocent learning and family connection, rendered in soft watercolor textures with characteristic Ghibli warmth and whimsy.
